{"title":"迎春曲——街头诗一束（下）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——街头诗一束（下）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高山在说话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上开了花，山在说话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我原来也是一座童山、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能把我压住的不是石头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是巨人的双手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能把我唤醒的不是风砂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是英雄的脚步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕种时站一站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闲时少一顿饭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间就是金子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳就是财产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人定胜天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天冷冷不了热心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地冻冻不了决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰雪盖不住信心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风吹不倒恒心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们说：人定胜天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动的人是万能。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野上扯起闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看那银光闪闪——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那儿真的是闪电？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是无数的铁铣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在几分钟的时间以内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一道上陵劈碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给果木队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年栽下一棵桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他年桃子吃不了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新栽起千亩果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果树数也难数了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要唱起迎春曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"预祝你们的收获！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要我们有了决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们能把荒山搬掉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在万年的岩层下面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能把“龙王”捉到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题防风林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要搭起天梯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和风砂展开大战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是天梯？那就是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丛林和翠绿的树枝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒滩和苹果树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这块荒滩上面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要说没有珍宝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几年前栽的苹果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是比珍宝还要好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒滩栽上金子树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树枝上飞起金鸟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王老汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——赠南水泉农业社的一位社员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王老汉的一双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几条裂痕像山沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他照常挖着大渠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手不停地挥着土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他还是从早到晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸笑容不发愁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说愚公能移山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他比愚公更能干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是一个独身汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果园和他结了伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他给人们栽下多少果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己吃的果子才几颗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看人间的乐园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在社员的身旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要锄头一敲响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"园门就对我们开放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向日葵摇着金杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红海棠能制果浆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们，把金杯举起吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设地上的天堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、水有路，土有家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头就要大搬家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想上开了门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难见到咱们怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看东风压倒西风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定叫今年胜过去年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给我们一枝金箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它一定要射穿荒原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给射手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要寻获一只牡鹿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要不怕走艰险的路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最高的山巅之上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牡鹿主才回一下头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田间还积着冰雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷鸟还没有啼叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一批敲响山谷的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能够把布谷鸟找到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们也在唱着布谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们就是那布谷鸟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年2月，写于南水泉"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}